"org\" type=\"http\">sito di Xfce</ulink>."

#: xfdesktop.xml:679(para)
msgid ""
"To report a bug or make a suggestion regarding this application or this "
"manual, use the bug tracking system at <ulink url=\"http://bugzilla.xfce.org/"
